{"tid":547192,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A]  龍珠z 爆裂大戰 頂住呀各位!\"","createTime":"2018-02-01T08:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T10:13:05.000Z","uid":146667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"beeca4e207a2552973746ba8e28489e49cabd49e","tid":547192,"uid":146667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"b]<span style=\"font-size: large;\">鍾意用台/陸譯名既唔該過主</span>[/b]<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5ctlse2k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5ctlse2k&h=0f7fb24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Credit 連狗巴打</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">活動</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5p4wsf2z\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5p4wsf2z&h=5294e488&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7s18x4a0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7s18x4a0&h=93be8300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pm8ixfol\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpm8ixfol&h=1f28dcb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">卡池</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oit57yxk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foit57yxk&h=1e369cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〜 2018/03/09 16:00 (香港時間)<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u623lfci\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu623lfci&h=1ffccd30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n〜 2018/02/01 16:00 (香港時間)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Q&amp;A</span></span></strong><br />\nQ. 綠石秘寶打邊關多？<br />\nA. 24-7<br />\n---<br />\nQ. 潛解行邊條路先？<br />\nA. 會10技既右下，唔會既左上 (右下&gt;左上&gt;右上&gt;左下)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">新手教學</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">感謝 冥幣巴整合</span></strong><br />\n其實你想知咩新手資料???大部分巴哈都有<br />\n<br />\n1. 每日我建議新手打龜仙人、Satan武道會、雲上活動，之後去攞獎品<br />\n2. 如果係升Rank嘅，<del>我估大家現在都係以力隊為主</del>，請趁現在3倍經驗解主線<del>Easy解到21-1(目覚めたさきに)</del>，之後再解到<del>呢關</del>最高難度，<del>力隊超4悟打體波易到爆</del>，順便刷綠石(打蘭芝同畢拉夫)換下新手角<br />\n3. 如果係打覺醒料，可以去覺醒活動關打<br />\n4. 升到D卡咁上下，請先去解超本氣果關，每日打潛力解放材料<br />\n(開放條件:<br />\nA. Rank 50以上<br />\nB.「超本気の超決戦」ステージ2.激突！超サイヤ人孫悟空のZ-HARD Clear)<br />\n5. 三倍經驗完左可以去刷每日強襲角，知、速角優先，刷的意思係講每隻刷10隻刷到10技，再刷多隻5技放倉，準備以後解超強襲.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">角色代號</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">感謝 格劍巴整合代號名單</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8of6x7b3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8of6x7b3&h=edec8fbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">舊代號名單 感謝 photomore 巴打整合</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg&d=GUs28YvtHAy1mguTCgpNhNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5002b630\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/031403_0f8104b2440ce5433f5504d1e13acd65.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">限定點心紙</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">感謝新一日巴打整合</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/230308_4daa399dbd507aa174dd2498be0057be.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F230308_4daa399dbd507aa174dd2498b